{
  "stem": "15174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so what these relatives started doing was they hired the little fishing boats.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And these fishing boats started sailing around the ship, trying to find-- get a glimpse of their relatives.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's where I learned my first Spanish word, which was manana.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everybody was yelling manana, which meant, of course, tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Tomorrow you'll disembark, tomorrow, tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there were-- it was-- it was a scene, a real scene.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "All these fishing boats just circling around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember one-- one time, I was standing on the deck and, of course, there was a big crowd of people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody was trying to see if they could recognize their relatives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I saw my aunts and uncles and my cousin Edith in this little boat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I started screaming Edith, Edith, Edith.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and this woman, who was standing next to me, said-- looked over to me and she said, why don't you shut up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I have more important things to yell to my relatives than you have to yell to yours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So be quiet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I also remember that not only did the fishing boats come out with relatives, but they-- some of the Cuban kids came out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they would dive into the water-- I guess people started throwing money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They would dive in the water and retrieve the-- the money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So this-- it was really a spectacle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, people would throw some money over, and these kids would dive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And it was a-- I remember that very well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "One day, my parents and I were standing on deck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we-- we saw my relatives in this little fishing boat.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
